These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, metal, dubstep, blues
House: victorian, cottage, futuristic, palace, wooden
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, november, july, december, august
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the futuristic house is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 3. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the fan of metal is the fan of metal##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is the victorian house##1
 6. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
10. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the fan of blues is between the chinese and the wooden house##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the cottage house##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Music-Genre      | electronic        | salsa | blues     | metal   | dubstep |
| House   | futuristic     | cottage      | palace | wooden   | victorian    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| Birthday           | november | july      | august     | december   | september     |

