.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
City: colone, hamburg, london, prague, venice
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, fonseca, oliveros, cain, old-henry
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, bellflower, daisy, begonia
 1. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is between the prince-smoker and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person who growsdaisy is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is the person traveling to london##1
12. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| City         | prague | colone | venice    | hamburg  | london    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Cigar   | old-henry   | fonseca     | prince    | cain  | oliveros     |
| Flower     | bellflower    | aconite | begonia | daisy | sunflower |

