.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, polish, australian, russian, british
5 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, turtle
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, june, august, november, january
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
 4. the indian is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the indian is on the right of the polish##1
 9. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the russian##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
13. the person who's birthday is in january is between the british and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | british  | polish | indian | russian | australian        |
| Pet   | goat      | chinchilla      | guinea-pig       | turtle       | horse       |
| Birthday         | june | january  | november    | december    | august        |

