.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, ritmeester, baccarat, game, old-henry
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, paramedic, software-developer, firefighter, lawyer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, sailing, surfing, lacrosse, cycling
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the scientist is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the game-smoker##2
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the software-developer##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the software-developer is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the lawyer is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the british##1
11. the firefighter is on the right of the software-developer##1
12. the british is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
13. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Cigar          | old-henry  | baccarat     | game   | ritmeester     | pall-mall |
| Job         | lawyer | scientist    | software-developer  | firefighter | paramedic   |
