The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, march, september, august, june
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the colonial house##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 8. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the colonial house##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the colonial house##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
