5 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, frog, dog, pony
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, australian, french, polish, turkish
5 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, scrabble, go, whist
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the french##1
 5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person who growstulip is between the owner of the pony and the person playing monopoly##2
 7. the person playing scrabble is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the frog is on the right of the french##1
10. the person playing go is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the pony and the person playing monopoly##2
12. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the polish##1
13. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Flower      | zinnia  | tulip      | balloon-flower   | begonia   | amaryllis   |
| Pet   | pony    | dog   | frog   | rat | goldfish     |
| Nationality   | argentine | french     | polish   | turkish | australian |
