There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, malaysian, argentine, chinese, russian
There 5 different types of food: spinach, lemon, garlic, onion, artichoke
5 different games are played: canasta, bridge, chess, poker, snooker
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, train, trike, van
 1. the person playing snooker is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person playing bridge##2
 2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 3. the malaysian is the person eating onion##1
 4. the egyptian is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the malaysian##1
 6. the person eating onion is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person eating garlic is on the left of the malaysian##1
 9. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
10. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the person playing chess and the person eating garlic##2
12. the chinese is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
13. the argentine is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Nationality    | argentine       | chinese    | russian | malaysian  | egyptian        |
| Food       | artichoke | spinach | garlic  | onion | lemon    |
| Game       | chess        | poker   | bridge  | snooker   | canasta |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

