.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, bellflower, poppy, rose
City: miami, london, hamburg, marseilles, venice
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
House: tower, colonial, art-deco, townhouse, farmhouse
 1. the art-deco house is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person watching crime movies and the person traveling to hamburg##2
 3. the person who growspoppy is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is between the person traveling to venice and the colonial house##2
 7. the townhouse house is the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person who growstulip is the art-deco house##1
 9. the tower house is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
10. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person traveling to hamburg is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Flower      | tulip      | daisy         | poppy      | bellflower | rose     |
| City           | london | hamburg | marseilles | venice    | miami  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| House   | art-deco  | colonial        | tower   | townhouse    | farmhouse     |

