.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daisy, azalea, amaryllis, dahlia
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, videographer, architect, journalist, mechanic
House: farmhouse, townhouse, gothic-revival, tower, wooden
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the wooden house is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the journalist is on the left of the videographer##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the townhouse house is between the designer and the farmhouse house##2
 6. the designer is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growsazalea is between the person driving the airplane and the person who growsdahlia##2
 8. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growssunflower##2
 9. the tower house is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Flower         | dahlia  | azalea | amaryllis   | daisy      | sunflower |
| Job   | designer   | journalist    | videographer | mechanic | architect      |
| House           | gothic-revival | townhouse    | farmhouse       | tower     | wooden      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

