.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
There 5 different types of food: lettuce, watermelon, tomato, scrabble-climbing, carrot
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
5 different games are played: canasta, billiard, domino, chess, scrabble
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, golf, tennis, rowing, lacrosse
 1. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person playing scrabble##2
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person playing canasta##1
 5. the person playing canasta is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person playing domino##2
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person playing chess##1
 8. the person eating scrabble-climbing is the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person playing billiard##1
10. the person eating scrabble-climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Food         | tomato    | carrot  | watermelon  | lettuce      | scrabble-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Game   | domino | canasta    | scrabble    | chess       | billiard         |
| Sport   | rowing  | golf | lacrosse    | tennis     | skateboarding      |

 